    <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
      <body> 
        <div rend="parallel">
            <p xml:id="Aink413-kilavi">ituvumatu.</p>
<p xml:lang="en">And this is that.</p>
</div>
        <div rend="parallel">
                <lg xml:id="Aink413">
                    <l>niṉṉuta ṉāṟu naṟuntaṇ puṟavi</l>
                    <l>niṉṉē pōla maññai yālak</l>
                    <l>kārtoṭaṅ kiṉṟāṟ poḻutē</l>
                    <l>pēriya larivai nānayat takavē.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg xml:lang="en">
            <l>In the fragrant cool woodland, as fragrant as your forehead,</l>
            <l>as the peacocks dance just like you,</l>
            <l>the time of the rainy season has indeed begun</l>
            <l>[in a way] fit for our desire, O great-natured young woman.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </body>
    </text>
